title: Care by physicians, non-physician clinicians does not differ in community health centers

title_detail.value: Care by physicians, non-physician clinicians does not differ in community health centers

summary: A new study examining patient health outcomes in community health centers found that nurse practitioners and physician assistants delivered care that was equivalent to care delivered by physicians.
